This LaTeX version of _why's poignant Guide to Ruby was crafted by the
mad Ruby (yml-parsing) skills of Michael Specht, who kindly gave me the tex
source. This repo hosts my tweaks of Michael's tex source.

Michael's original post can be found at:
http://www.thinkingaloud.net/whys-poignant-guide-to-ruby/

A copy of _why's project is at
http://poignant.rubyforge.org/

An working HTML version seems to be hosted on
http://mislav.uniqpath.com/poignant-guide/

Distributed under the Creative Common's Attribute-ShareAlike license
in respect of _why's choice of license.
